content: yungalgo: Merged four pull requests in elizaos/eliza, including a major refactor to centralize directory detection logic (#5246, +6421/-2262) and a feature for agent-scoped plugins (#5270) that was later rolled back (#5297). This work involved 53 commits across 162 files, resulting in a net change of +5264/-4421 lines. They also provided feedback through 11 PR comments and 2 code reviews.
